Ibinigay ni Feng Suige ang punyal na ito

00:36:05.400 --> 00:36:06.150
sa akin.

00:36:06.320 --> 00:36:07.640
Kinuha niya ito.

00:36:07.840 --> 00:36:08.400
Guro,

00:36:08.420 --> 00:36:09.420
