00:36:09.550 --> 00:36:11.680
Pinipilit lang niyang magkaroon ng punyal na ito!

00:36:18.150 --> 00:36:18.760
Qin!

00:36:19.230 --> 00:36:20.430
Qin, okay ka lang?

